{"tid":927098,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大種乞兒] 14歲賣藝童嫌收入少掟篋洩憤 擾及內地魔術師捱打","createTime":"2018-12-04T02:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T03:41:59.000Z","uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"505ebf88f65b8ce8daa1b868211d46315a436d9e","tid":927098,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:41:37.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀發生街頭賣藝童被打事件。一名姓蘇（14歲）男童，昨日（3日）晚上10時許，在星光行對開表演「扯鈴」時，疑因僅賺得百餘元打賞錢，較過往少百餘元，大發脾氣，將裝載工具的行李篋亂掟洩憤，卻擾及毗鄰一名姓王（24歲）內地男子表演魔術，雙方頓起爭執，他被人用手機扑傷頭部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nKL7z0klV4.m4rPqAcQYGg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/08a06406af14d216a6eedf254b01af9f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnKL7z0klV4.m4rPqAcQYGg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F08a06406af14d216a6eedf254b01af9f&h=ce19b8b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員接報到場調查後，以涉嫌襲擊致造成身體實際傷害將王拘捕，蘇童其後由父親陪同下，由救護車送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n蘇童在醫院表示，他是中三學生，有數年「扯鈴」經驗，在現場星光行外表演約一年，每星期演出4至5晚。對方內地表演者只擺檔數天，相信今次是因他「發脾氣」導致被打。他又稱，收入不佳令心情欠佳，故將器材擲落地，因此擾及對方。他正考慮稍後由父親陪同向警方銷案，不追究事件。<br />\n<br />\n在蘇童的facebook可見他自幼已學懂「扯鈴」，並貼有大批以往公開表演的照片，亦曾經獲得獎項。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NFlyzAylUmBlcrCC3ZIH0g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/6b8ee790c417b9a059656bc62b165d8b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNFlyzAylUmBlcrCC3ZIH0g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F6b8ee790c417b9a059656bc62b165d8b&h=29ad103c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據資料，「扯鈴」是一種中國傳統音響玩具，發源於北京一帶。「扯鈴」是一個底面圓形、側面雙凹的木質物體。玩者是用一根兩端有把手的繩抖動、轉動或拋起「扯鈴」，具有很強觀賞性，可以強身健體。傳統的中國扯「扯鈴」有挖哨，隨着旋轉速度加快會發出聲音；在外國又稱中國溜溜球，而歐美所使用的「扯鈴」一般以較軟的塑膠材質製成，沒有哨，不會因為發聲而消耗能量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3bhRxaypnYKscyRE7ffHOg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/a2c26483141662ea7a3c362db1d4ade0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3bhRxaypnYKscyRE7ffHOg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fa2c26483141662ea7a3c362db1d4ade0&h=fbdbd64e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b69157c7c667e359c468b61e20b8fe7cea4724b","tid":927098,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"佢好有heart，成日路德圍見佢表演"},{"pid":"1e068f3abfa09f6a595590c7ebd2b3d48e02fd62","tid":927098,"uid":9457,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"9b69157c7c667e359c468b61e20b8fe7cea4724b","tid":927098,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"佢好有heart，成日路德圍見佢表演"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"咁我都好有heart 日日都返工"},{"pid":"4e1e1bbf1c8a8f423dd35669b558171fc9996d77","tid":927098,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b69157c7c667e359c468b61e20b8fe7cea4724b","tid":927098,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"佢好有heart，成日路德圍見佢表演"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:50:55.000Z","msg":"但真係好撚臭脾氣咼....<br />\n見佢成日西面...掟野 (可能觀眾反應唔好)<br />\n不過係香港街頭表演就預左反應冷淡咖啦<br />\n仲成日想同觀眾互動  想人打叫比反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到比錢...就更加好笑 <br />\n香港人食花生就叻 睇完就走咖啦<br />\nbtw 有無人知佢點解要講英文"},{"pid":"ac8f8af48751c0036e898da788e1a1406f62dddb","tid":927098,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e068f3abfa09f6a595590c7ebd2b3d48e02fd62","tid":927098,"uid":9457,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"9b69157c7c667e359c468b61e20b8fe7cea47